   446→
   447→                      <div className="space-y-2 text-sm">
   448→                        <div className="p-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900/50">
   449→                          <p className="font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-1">
   450→                            Attivita a casa:
